<p class="geolocation-title">This winter, enjoy a ski holiday to the spectacularly beautiful <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff</a> and enjoy the ski experience of skiing three incredible ski areas.</p>
<p class="geolocation-title">Book your holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/c5a8431a4b9c4e3fb820365f26d278bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5a8431a4b9c4e3fb820365f26d278bb}" title="Banff Inn Hotel">Banff Inn Hotel</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13}" title="Banff Ptarmigan Inn">Banff Ptarmigan Inn</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/37c974a0e942433782b7f7c66871db2b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37c974a0e942433782b7f7c66871db2b}" title="Brewsters Mountain Lodge">Brewsters Mountain Lodge</a> in Banff between 1 October - 30 November 2017 and receive £100 discount per couple on selected departure 1-25th March 2018. What's more, this offer can be combined with all other Banff offers!</p>
